  we live in a security context which is   very difficult  to the west we have an implacable enemy  we have fought four wars  with  that  country    even  now  it  persists  in  trying  to  hurt  us  by  using irregulars  and  terrorists      to  the  north  we  have  a  very  strong  enemy    all  our attempts to stabilize that border to even draw up the line of actual control have failed  because  of  the  obduracy  of  china      therefore  we  have  to  be  ready  for  a twofront  war  we have  to strengthen  our  forces  keeping  this security  context in mind    our  modernization  and  strengthening  of  our  forces  are  proceeding  apace  we need to strengthen our army our navy and our air force  i believe and our party believes that our defence comes first and foremost and for that finances will never  be  a  problem    that  is  something  which  we  will  stand  by  and  we  aim  at achieving  a  capability  which  will  deter  and  if  necessary  defeat  any  of  our adversaries   